  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/System\/Errno\/noMessage\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T22:03:39Z\n---\n\n# noMessage\n\n**Type Property**\n\nNo message of desired type.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nstatic var noMessage: Errno { get }\n```\n\n## Discussion\n\nAn IPC message queue doesn’t contain a message of the desired type, or a message catalog doesn’t contain the requested message.\n\nThe corresponding C error is `ENOMSG`.\n\n## General Errors\n\n- **badMessage**: Bad message.\n- **canceled**: Operation canceled.\n- **illegalByteSequence**: Illegal byte sequence.\n- **noData**: No message available.\n- **noSuchPolicy**: No such policy registered.\n- **notPermitted**: Operation not permitted.\n- **notRecoverable**: State not recoverable.\n- **outputQueueFull**: Interface output queue is full.\n- **tooManyReferences**: Too many references: can’t splice.\n- **tooManyUsers**: Too many users.\n\n",
